Package com.example.androidgpt_pro

Class EventCard

java.lang.Object
com.example.androidgpt_pro.EventCard
public class EventCard extends Object
This class handles the Event Cards to be placed in the Events List in the Browse Events screen. Populates card with event poster and basic event information
